	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/27000/indexMediumPc2/27000.jpg?1463548673" alt="马竞打进了欧冠决赛，身为股东的万达会高兴吗？">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/3/medium/3.png?1411569578" alt="娱乐">
			<span>娱乐</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">马竞打进了欧冠决赛，身为股东的万达会高兴吗？</h1>
